casebody.data:
CITY OF BOWLING GREEN, KENTUCKY, et al.,
v.
Carey WOODCOCK, as Administratrix of the Estate of Gregory Harrison, Deceased. No. 16-1500 (R46-017). Supreme Court of the United States Aug. 16, 2017.

The petition for writ of certiorari was dismissed today pursuant to Rule 46.1 of the Rules of this Court.
